examples.en: He had trouble balancing on his skis.
They treated the running surface of the skis with dope.
He gave the attic a good rummage but couldn't find his skis.
She said that five small boys on skis was a recipe for disaster, not a holiday.
They trekked towards the North Pole with sleds and skis.
Five small boys on skis is a recipe for disaster (=is very likely to end badly).
